column5: Finally getting to hit the ice and try for some 'eyes. Was out last night and got into a feeding frenzy of these beauts...for 45 minutes it was pure insanity...what a night...    Can't wait to get back out on Sunday...
lets see what am I doing Sunday...LOL nice going  real nice looking fish there
Nice fish. Bookends! Are you in the Ottawa River below Ottawa or above?  Dan O.
Not the Ottawa river actually, one of the many awesome lakes that dot the region....pretty sweet fishery
Those are some great walleyes for the Ottawa Area, great work!
Nicely done Matt   Sounds like fun   congrats
